{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>STORY:</strong></h2>Fred's car breaks down in the middle of a forest, forcing him to seek help. But he soon discovers that something else is going on. Your goal in this text-based choice game is to help the protagonist survive until he uncovers the mysteries of this place and reunites with his daughter, Susan.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186200/extras/img_desc_1.png?t=1736264161\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>6+ DIFFERENT ENDINGS</strong></h2>There are many paths that you can choose and lead to more than 6 different endings. Some good and others bad.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186200/extras/img_desc_2.png?t=1736264161\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>IMMERSIVE GAMEPLAY</strong></h2>Many places to visit with images of all the regions of the game. Gameplay full of sounds for better fill the ambience and what is happening at the momment.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>SURVIVAL MECHANICS</strong></h2>You are controlling a person, keep that in mind if you want Fred to survive his journey. With health and hunger meters, mainten then filled up by using itens from your inventory.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186200/extras/img_desc_4.gif?t=1736264161\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>FULL TRANSLATION TO ENGLISH AND PORTUGUESE</strong></h2>The game contains full translation for both english and brazilian portuguese. And plans for even more languages in the future!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186200/extras/img_desc_5.gif?t=1736264161\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Blood Pool","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3186200/14eddc811c22f42a6113e2ebeb8e155af3672688.jpg"},{"name":"No Energy","path":"https